{"tid":224331,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《異形5》開拍希望渺茫 只有構思沒劇本","createTime":"2017-05-01T03:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T13:35:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"784c819589eb5f822acb8e2343a0adbde83e8e2f","tid":224331,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"《異形：契約》馬上就要上映了，以現在大家對這部電影的關注程度，相信該片上映之後票房一定不會差。不過，另一部片子就沒那麼好的命運了，擱置已久的《異形5》還是沒有進展，就就連身為製作人的雷老都直接無視了：連個劇本都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n近日，在接受法國媒體的採訪時，雷老透露了自己關於《異形5》的看法：&ldquo;我覺得開拍的希望很渺茫，至今都還沒有劇本，只是一些點子、構想罷了。整個項目並沒有進展，因為福斯根本就沒打算要拍。就我而言，普羅米修斯系列就是目前的重點。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n除了《異形：契約》外，《普羅米修斯》三部曲的下一部疑似定名為《覺醒》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170430/5/48/2/異形5-開拍希望渺茫-只有構思沒劇本拍個毛線-7332510.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170430%2F5%2F48%2F2%2F%E7%95%B0%E5%BD%A25-%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E6%B8%BA%E8%8C%AB-%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%A7%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%B2%92%E5%8A%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%8B%8D%E5%80%8B%E6%AF%9B%E7%B7%9A-7332510.html&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6fc80f66\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170430/5/48/2/異形5-開拍希望渺茫-只有構思沒劇本拍個毛線-7332510.html</a>"},{"pid":"0ba9c15efd7f409ffa2e1e633477ffa4ae536233","tid":224331,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"無就拍District 10啦"},{"pid":"15aa262cad5f8f33acaabfdcbcf90b453d1e2b9a","tid":224331,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"拍AVP3啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e76dc55f596e358a566f158b8b737457bf2387","tid":224331,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無就拍District 10啦</blockquote><br />\n一早要啦..<br />\n等左咁多年 仲未有氣息<br />\n無啦啦仲走去拍異形5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44de